## Adding a New Subsystem Checklist

When proposing a new subsystem, it must have:

- [ ] A `Base` class or `Protocol` defining the interface
- [ ] An entry in `app/dependencies.py` (DI)
- [ ] At least one unit test with mocked I/O
- [ ] A health check endpoint contribution or status field in `/api/health`
- [ ] Startup + shutdown hooks in `lifespan`
- [ ] Structured log entries with component name field
- [ ] Resource estimate: RAM, CPU, open connections

